If you want to check to see if there <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>are</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> random variations in the % mana saved, then strip off nearly all your gear and cast your most expensive appropriate spell.  When I have, I always get exactly the same number of spell casts.  With none of the mana saving focus items have I ever seen any variation in the number of times I can cast a particular spell on a full mana bar, barring fizzles.<br>
