<br>
I havnt tested anything myself, but my own observations in group xp grinding are that some part of the savings (be it specialization, scm, or the focus earring) seems to be random for nukes, because some nukes take a far different amount of mana than others.  Im pretty sure that people have observed with ODS and other focuses that the amount they save is random (correct me if im worng).<br>
